  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/2c09b4401aee096a87cdd95d07917051.poster.avif?t=1734674904\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/2c09b4401aee096a87cdd95d07917051.webm?t=1734674904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/2c09b4401aee096a87cdd95d07917051.mp4?t=1734674904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fresh take on Roguelike Deckbuilding Classics<br></li><li><strong>12 characters</strong> from 4 classes to create your team<br></li><li>Over <strong>700 cards</strong>, <strong>160 Talents</strong>, <strong>90 enemies</strong>, and <strong>50 items</strong><br></li><li>Deckbuilding agility to <strong>replace cards</strong> or <strong>enhance them with <strong>Runes</strong><br></strong></li><li>High <strong>replay value</strong> due to procedural generation for each run<br></li><li>Paths with <strong>story events</strong> and <strong>mini-games</strong> entertainment<br></li><li><strong>Deep lore</strong> of Mekaa history and <strong>character story</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/c91baae9b044280f33c585ea533cd450.poster.avif?t=1734674904\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/c91baae9b044280f33c585ea533cd450.webm?t=1734674904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/c91baae9b044280f33c585ea533cd450.mp4?t=1734674904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/b78ad43dd45124d9269ea745b628e032.avif?t=1734674904\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br>Choose from <strong>12 characters</strong> to make the team. Each char has <strong>their own and class’ cards, mechanics, and stats</strong>. While a hero sets up the main direction, it is your choice whom to invite to the party — debuffer, card spammer, or fire healer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/438a2b1fd61c87b3e2cafa3b6d276f4e.avif?t=1734674904\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br><strong>Over 700 cards</strong> that can be combined with <strong>Runes</strong>, procedurally generated tree from <strong>160 Talents</strong>, and <strong>50 items</strong> — all at your hands to face over <strong>90 different enemies</strong>. Replace cards and adjust your deck on the go.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/ab4858f242845f76972f05bca2ff0f09.avif?t=1734674904\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br>Continent Mekaa has a <strong>rich history</strong>, pieces of which you learn playing the Adventure mode. Each of the <strong>playable characters also has their own Story</strong> that lets you live through the most meaningful times of their lives.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/26c380a74cf4626f0e0fb5406a688728.avif?t=1734674904\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br>Indies’ Lies is a journey in the <strong>Dark Fantasy Steampunk</strong> world. You fight your way in the world on the verge between Medieval times and the industrial revolution. Complete <strong>Camp quests</strong>, play many <strong>mini-games</strong>, and discover <strong>on-map events</strong>  — each game will be different!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/9b84c8a9cb1a5f155329d6ff4408fbbd.poster.avif?t=1734674904\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/9b84c8a9cb1a5f155329d6ff4408fbbd.webm?t=1734674904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/9b84c8a9cb1a5f155329d6ff4408fbbd.mp4?t=1734674904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
